00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:40.000
Keneth Branagh directs the sci-fi movie Thor, based on the Marvel comics and 

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.000
inspired by the homonymous Scandinavian god.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:46.000
Chris Hemsworth plays Thor, a brave but arrogant god,

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.000
who is exiled to the earth by his father Odin

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.000
and forced to live among humans.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.000
There he meets the scientist, Jane Foster,

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:56.000
who will help him become a true hero and face his half-brother Loki,

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.000
who wants to invade our planet.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.000
The film will be released in Italy on April 29.

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:05.000
The 36th edition of the French César Awards

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:09.000
will be held in Paris on February 25 ans will be chaired by the actress Jodie Foster.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:14.000
The last time there was a foreign chairman in 1993,

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
it was Marcello Mastroianni.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:19.000
A real honor for the actress!

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:20.000
